      "related_files": [
        "goseg/main.go"
      ],
      "evidence": [
        "`main.init()` panics if embedded web assets cannot be prepared (`panic(err)`), while `main()` treats several subsystem initializers as recoverable by logging and continuing (`exporter.Initialize`, `importer.Initialize`, `broadcast.Initialize`, `docker.Initialize`).",
        "Only configuration initialization terminates `main` early; other similar failures proceed to server startup and runtime routines."
      ],
